quran[8{c,v,t}:
48,16,jo ganwar peechay reh gay they un se keh do ke tum aik sakht jangju qoum ke ( sath larai ke ) liye bulaye jao ge un se tum ( ya to ) jung karte raho ge ya woh islam le ayen ge. agar tum hukum manu ge to khuda tum ko acha badla day ga. aur agar munh phair lau ge jaisay pehli dafaa phera tha to woh tum ko buri takleef ki saza day ga
48,17,nah to andhay par gunah hai ( ke safar jung se peechay reh jaye ) aur nah lngrhe par gunah hai aur nah bemaar par gunah hai. aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke paighambar ke farmaan par chalay ga khuda is ko bahishtoon mein daakhil kere ga jin ke taley nehrain beh rahi hain. aur jo rogrdani kere ga usay buray dukh ki saza day ga
48,18,( ae paighambar ) jab momin tum se darakht ke neechay baet kar rahay they to khuda un se khush howa. aur jo ( Sadaq o khaloos ) un ke dilon mein tha woh is ne maloom karliya. to un par tasalii nazil farmai aur inhen jald fatah inayat ki
48,19,aur bohat si ghanimatainjo unhon ne haasil kee. aur khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
48,20,khuda ne tum se bohat si ghanimaton ka wada farmaya ke tum un ko haasil karo ge so is ne ghanemat ki tumahray liye jaldi farmai aur logon ke haath tum se rok diye. gharz yeh thi ke yeh mominoun ke liye ( khuda ki ) qudrat ka namona ho aur woh tum ko seedhay raste par chalaye
48,21,aur aur ( ghanimatainden ) jin par tum qudrat nahi rakhtay they ( aur ) woh khuda hi ki qudrat mein theen. aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
48,22,aur agar tum se kafir lartay to peeth phair kar bhaag jatay phir kisi ko dost nah paate aur nah madadgaar
48,23,( yahi ) khuda ki aadat hai jo pehlay se chali aati hai. aur tum khuda ki aadat kabhi badalti nah dekho ge
